.SS "#define ENGINE_API   __attribute__((visibility('default')))"

.PP
Cross-platform export macro for DLL/shared library definitions\&. On Windows platforms, this macro expands to __declspec(dllexport) to properly export symbols from a dynamic library\&. On other platforms (Linux, macOS), it expands to nothing, allowing the code to work seamlessly across different OS\&.

.PP
Usage: 
.PP
.nf
class ENGINE_API MyPublicClass { \&.\&.\&. };

.fi
